13. UX / UI Notes
- Query UI: top answer with confidence + 'Show Sources' button that expands to list of chunks with file/page/snippet and link to download original.
- Ingestion dashboard: shows queue, ingestion time, error messages, and retry button.

14. Roadmap & Milestones
- M1 (4 weeks): Core ingestion, embeddings pipeline, vector index, basic UI, auth.
- M2 (8 weeks): Improved QA prompts, auditability, pagination & filtering, export functionality.
- M3 (12+ weeks): SSO, RBAC, admin console, enterprise readiness.

15. Operational Runbook (short)
- Monitor `ingestion_queue_depth` and `query_latency_p95`.
- If ingestion fails repeatedly: inspect worker logs, check embedding provider rate limits and storage availability.

16. Risks & Mitigations
- Embedding costs: mitigate with batching, open-source models, and cost caps per org.
- Incorrect answers / hallucinations: provide provenance, human-in-the-loop verification, and conservative answer templates showing sources.

17. Open Questions
- Which embedding provider(s) do we target for v1? (OpenAI, Azure, local models)
- Retention policy and export/archival requirements per customer?

